    description: "Ana is an experienced yoga teacher, certified yoga therapist (C-IAYT), and teacher training faculty member based in Vancouver, BC. With E-RYT 500 certification and over 15 years of full-time teaching, Ana brings deep expertise and warm approachability to every class. Her instruction is centered around the breath, offering insights inspired by the five elements and yogic deities that lead to inner reflection, always delivered with a healthy dash of humor. Ana offers private yoga sessions, group classes, and corporate yoga programs throughout Vancouver. Her private sessions are available by direct message through her active Instagram community of nearly 10,000 followers. As a C-IAYT certified yoga therapist, Ana is qualified to work with students managing health conditions and seeking therapeutic applications of yoga practice.",
